<h3 id="installation">Installation</h3>

<p>Step 1. Download the file <a href="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/jhvanderschee/jekyllcodex/gh-pages/_includes/follow-buttons.html">follow-buttons.html</a>
<br />Step 2. Save the file in the ‘_includes’ directory of your project
<br />Step 3. Make sure the bottom of your layout document looks like this:</p>

<pre><code>...
{% include follow-buttons.html %}
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</code></pre>
<p>Step 4. Add the following variables to your ‘_config.yml’ file (with value’s):</p>
<pre><code>facebook_url: 
twitter_url: 
linkedin_url: 
googleplus_url:
pinterest_url:
instagram_url:
</code></pre>
